Allianz Field Application #88368035






Application Filed: 2019-04-02

Trademark Application Details





The mark consists of the words "ALLIANZ FIELD" in stylized font separated by a circle with the stylized image of an eagle formed by three vertical lines inside the circle.
Mark For: ALLIANZ FIELD® trademark registration is intended to cover the categories of arena services, namely, providing general purpose facilities for sports, concerts, conventions and exhibitions; Arena services, namely, providing general purpose stadium facilities for sports, concerts, conventions, and exhibitions where the aforementioned events may be broadcast over television, radio, and other media distribution.
